snippet.title: Holdfast: Nations At War - Austrian Empire! Released
snippet.description:
The long awaited Austrians finally arrive! Ram your shot and prepare for battle, the Austrian nation marches into Holdfast with this major update release.
- Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/589290/Holdfast_Nations_At_War/
